3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T06:51:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>住澳洲邊度？</blockquote><br />\nAdelaide<br />\n住到人都癲</blockquote><br />\n點解？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講住係個邊d人好撚癲 (精神方面)"},{"pid":"1c3cb44f640df5f66fd1a19a3f480bf939d53914","tid":493963,"uid":143206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T06:53:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>住澳洲邊度？</blockquote><br />\nAdelaide<br />\n住到人都癲</blockquote><br />\n點解？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講住係個邊d人好撚癲 (精神方面)</blockquote><br />\nwhy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7b41326b49885bc3e577b5e1156a028f87eb2a","tid":493963,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T06:53:35.000Z","msg":"後唔後悔返黎發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9627afbe9090d806db26c95315ffebe95475d7","tid":493963,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T06:54:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>後唔後悔返黎發<span style=\"color: red;\">現</span>展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4fc4f5b5900f4dfdb9f5ec1856445316eec61a85","tid":493963,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>後唔後悔返黎發<span style=\"color: red;\">現</span>展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n現你老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b3c966a9d8deba3f858c8a7cfa34c5b3419634","tid":493963,"uid":156549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T07:12:22.000Z","msg":"邊到多袋獸捉"},{"pid":"9fde0a601355e5702793de41752aceaceece6fbf","tid":493963,"uid":85659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T07:23:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>住澳洲邊度？</blockquote><br />\nAdelaide<br />\n住到人都癲</blockquote><br />\n點解？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講住係個邊d人好撚癲 (精神方面)</blockquote><br />\nwhy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識幾個都係個度住<br />\n無論係人際、生活、工作<br />\n佢地都覺得香港好好多<br />\n<br />\n佢地會話行出街,周圍都好闊絡,夜少少就無哂人好似死城咁<br />\n但當你同佢講返香港近幾年中國禍害<br />\n好似人權、自由、生活條件同埋都市人查實都係咁生活<br />\n佢地好自然咁寧願龜返係個邊悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地覺得澳洲唔好既原因大部份都係覺得無人講香港話或者周街英文<br />\n<br />\n我仲諗住呢一兩年過去住下先查證到<br />\n澳洲近幾年好多中國人/華人/台勞移民過去搶工作<br />\n搞到係個邊生活除非搵得好,一般工作都係燒錢過日晨,住屋同食呢個問題分分鐘同香港無異,窮少少一係同台勞迫監倉,一係等政府養<br />\n<br />\n查實當佢地up得出:澳洲唔好得過香港去邊既時候,已經可以講有精神病,我遇過社工,政府人員都係癲癲地,好似洪朝豐咁"},{"pid":"a3797af5dc747ce28369e872940727e2dda0a9c8","tid":493963,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"幾時排蝗"},{"pid":"5e43649e245c6013578a0a2c5d2bb067992d3ff6","tid":493963,"uid":15219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T07:40:58.000Z","msg":"黎緊去Adelaide exchange巴打可唔可以講多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ec721bcc16809638b0c08277a43c8c53d669ea","tid":493963,"uid":155346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"留名 二月去Townsville 讀書"},{"pid":"29861c144e4b498f62acd58e915c74e3a4a2e3fe","tid":493963,"uid":114285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名 二月去Townsville 讀書</blockquote><br />\n去度咁遠？拎PR?"},{"pid":"cc349bbf7ac192e8251be89e9cf002edbfc199a4","tid":493963,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>住澳洲邊度？</blockquote><br />\nAdelaide<br />\n住到人都癲</blockquote><br />\n點解？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講住係個邊d人好撚癲 (精神方面)</blockquote><br />\nwhy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識幾個都係個度住<br />\n無論係人際、生活、工作<br />\n佢地都覺得香港好好多<br />\n<br />\n佢地會話行出街,周圍都好闊絡,夜少少就無哂人好似死城咁<br />\n但當你同佢講返香港近幾年中國禍害<br />\n好似人權、自由、生活條件同埋都市人查實都係咁生活<br />\n佢地好自然咁寧願龜返係個邊悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地覺得澳洲唔好既原因大部份都係覺得無人講香港話或者周街英文<br />\n<br />\n我仲諗住呢一兩年過去住下先查證到<br />\n澳洲近幾年好多中國人/華人/台勞移民過去搶工作<br />\n搞到係個邊生活除非搵得好,一般工作都係燒錢過日晨,住屋同食呢個問題分分鐘同香港無異,窮少少一係同台勞迫監倉,一係等政府養<br />\n<br />\n查實當佢地up得出:澳洲唔好得過香港去邊既時候,已經可以講有精神病,我遇過社工,政府人員都係癲癲地,好似洪朝豐咁</blockquote><br />\n咁言下之意你覺得澳洲點先，好唔好住"},{"pid":"3380a836cb2222f04ed464c13c1bb63e154dbb5f","tid":493963,"uid":65298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:18:07.000Z","msg":"who fucking cares"},{"pid":"34a2f709839ac33f9a806045c71a74d33642bfb0","tid":493963,"uid":12557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:20:59.000Z","msg":"係 Perth 住左10年<br />\n返左香港15 年<br />\n除左冶安同上網之外，我鍾意Aus 多d<br />\n香港周圍都太多人"},{"pid":"4e170a4a74039417ca8b55037e25f4572d2a95b4","tid":493963,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>住澳洲邊度？</blockquote><br />\nAdelaide<br />\n住到人都癲</blockquote><br />\n點解？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講住係個邊d人好撚癲 (精神方面)</blockquote><br />\nwhy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識幾個都係個度住<br />\n無論係人際、生活、工作<br />\n佢地都覺得香港好好多<br />\n<br />\n佢地會話行出街,周圍都好闊絡,夜少少就無哂人好似死城咁<br />\n但當你同佢講返香港近幾年中國禍害<br />\n好似人權、自由、生活條件同埋都市人查實都係咁生活<br />\n佢地好自然咁寧願龜返係個邊悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地覺得澳洲唔好既原因大部份都係覺得無人講香港話或者周街英文<br />\n<br />\n我仲諗住呢一兩年過去住下先查證到<br />\n澳洲近幾年好多中國人/華人/台勞移民過去搶工作<br />\n搞到係個邊生活除非搵得好,一般工作都係燒錢過日晨,住屋同食呢個問題分分鐘同香港無異,窮少少一係同台勞迫監倉,一係等政府養<br />\n<br />\n查實當佢地up得出:澳洲唔好得過香港去邊既時候,已經可以講有精神病,我遇過社工,政府人員都係癲癲地,好似洪朝豐咁</blockquote><br />\n咁言下之意你覺得澳洲點先，好唔好住</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天國</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">沒有華人的話</span>"},{"pid":"8344748136fb3b4b99fa2814330e8b09c4cde608","tid":493963,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:23:30.000Z","msg":"澳洲間屋幾大？<br />\n<br />\n香港間屋又幾大？"},{"pid":"40a035d513d1649f809c72ef422d01ba2bab8c2e","tid":493963,"uid":12557,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:39:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳洲間屋幾大？<br />\n<br />\n香港間屋又幾大？</blockquote><br />\n~4000 sq ft garage included<br />\nbackyard ~8000sq ft<br />\n香港2100sq ft&amp;800 sq ft frontyard(普通村屋)"},{"pid":"52ebc8fcb3178cf7c8cb17464fe63a27b34b046a","tid":493963,"uid":23705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咩返黎地獄呀？喺澳洲咪好囉</blockquote><br />\n澳洲搵唔到錢"},{"pid":"b66362d26946720f6a1cc39b446cf1ddc13a6c30","tid":493963,"uid":23705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:08:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇Tasmania</blockquote><br />\nIncest <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2569dc30d4ebb5723ad67e26dc57ea33df777c4a","tid":493963,"uid":23705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:08:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最易攞到pr既方法係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左娶澳洲妹</blockquote><br />\n娶/嫁澳洲基佬"},{"pid":"f5c00c0545d0309d52676c846c4f45f17b7a63ff","tid":49396